sub_title: Head of Sales and Market Research at Innowise
summary: With a master's degree in BA International Management and 8 years of professional experience, I bring expertise in sales, management, and business analysis. My diverse background has equipped me with strong management and organizational skills, as well as extensive IT knowledge. I thrive in dynamic environments and am a quick learner, able to adapt to new challenges with ease. I am a self-directed team player who values collaboration and thrives in a supportive environment. I am deeply committed to ongoing growth and development, both professionally and personally. I am also dedicated to spiritual growth.
